{"tid":287131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿根廷茅王後衛 用針拮對手贏波","createTime":"2017-06-17T07:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T00:56:51.000Z","uid":2862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f390fe837c1d6bfddab7a90281a37fcd4ce2b5b","tid":287131,"uid":2862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"周日阿根廷盃64強賽事，第6級別球隊帕西菲科爆大冷，作客阿甲球隊學生隊，以3:2贏波晉級。不過賽後仲有故講，帕西菲科嘅後衛艾蘭迪（Federico Allende）懶得戚，自爆話佢喺比賽期間不斷用針拮對手前鋒祖安奧迪路。<br />\n<br />\n艾蘭迪日前接受阿根廷電台訪問話：「佢（奧迪路）一定憎死我，但足球比賽就係咁，唔可以對對手仁慈，對住學生隊呢種級數嘅對手，乜嘢污糟手段都要用。」受害者奧迪路喺賽後亦有講呢件事，話比賽期間不斷被拮，向球證投訴但冇受理。<br />\n<br />\n咁都得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170617&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=56840602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170617%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D56840602&d=qBlL0UXXa5tvT3FCvVqNui7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=03a7c71d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170617%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D56840602&h=0b760645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170617&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=56840602</a><br />\n【沒有最卑鄙】阿根廷茅王後衛 用針拮對手贏波"},{"pid":"b7010a8d124a00f523eb12081455d6db891be64e","tid":287131,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:43:05.000Z","msg":"仲要爆響口"},{"pid":"7a8eaa99f16281caa2dc36a02ebb4e880101e977","tid":287131,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"點收埋"},{"pid":"f2567a6ee232396ed6c66b1c64ce2f737841b255","tid":287131,"uid":43967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:48:07.000Z","msg":"誠實豆沙包？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 足總應該會追究掛"},{"pid":"dfeb48c64da0b5df5be0c2431be31e3018a43129","tid":287131,"u